---


const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;

export interface Props {
  backgroundStyle?: string;
  id?: string;
}

const { backgroundStyle, id } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="pt-16" data-section-type="intro" id={id} style={backgroundStyle || 'background: var(--bg-graphite-charcoal-50);'}>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-graphite-charcoal-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="intro-welcome-text" data-delay="0.2">
          Welcome to WTI, where we transform complex challenges into impactful, secure, and data-driven solutions.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-welcome-text" data-delay="0.4">
          At WTI, we combine agility, intelligent workflows, and rapid execution to address today’s intricate mission demands. Our culture, rooted in partnership and trust, empowers us to leverage AI, data-driven insights, and technical expertise to consistently surpass expectations and drive mission success.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-welcome-text" data-delay="0.6">
          We deliver a dynamic mix of speed, agility, and expertise, turning challenges into secure, innovative outcomes. Our strength lies in our people—a dedicated team of experts, including a significant number of veterans and active DoD SkillBridge partners, all united by a commitment to excellence and teamwork.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-welcome-text" data-delay="0.8">
          Communication is our cornerstone. Our open-door policy fosters cohesion, energy, and relentless focus, ensuring every client mission is executed with precision.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-welcome-text" data-delay="1.0">
          More than just a contractor, WTI builds enduring partnerships grounded in transparency, innovation, and tangible results. As you explore our website, discover our proven record of delivering streamlined, innovative, solutions that uphold the highest standards of excellence and accountability.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 flex justify-start">
        <img src={`${baseUrl}CF_Signature.png`} alt="Cindy Ford Signature" class="h-16 w-auto intro-welcome-text" data-delay="1.4" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro-welcome-text {
    transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
  }
</style>

